<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Compliance Certificate</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #1f2937;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 48px 40px;
            background: white;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .letterhead {
            text-align: center;
            padding-bottom: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 36px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }

        .company-name {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #111827;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }

        .company-detail {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #4b5563;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .doc-title-wrap {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 32px 0;
        }

        .doc-title {
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #e5e7eb;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.06em;
        }

        .doc-subtitle {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #6b7280;
            margin-top: 4px;
        }

        .compliant-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 8px 24px;
            border-radius: 9999px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.06em;
            background: #ecfdf5;
            color: #059669;
            margin-top: 12px;
            border: 2px solid #059669;
        }

        .cert-meta {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 12px;
            margin: 28px 0;
        }

        .cert-meta-item {
            background: #f9fafb;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 10px 14px;
        }

        .cert-meta-item .label {
            font-size: 10px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.06em;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .cert-meta-item .value {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #111827;
            margin-top: 2px;
        }

        .entity-card {
            background: #f9fafb;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 24px 0;
        }

        .entity-label {
            font-size: 11px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.06em;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .entity-name {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #111827;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .entity-detail {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #4b5563;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .content {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #374151;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        .content p {
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .compliance-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin: 24px 0;
        }

        .compliance-table th {
            background: #f9fafb;
            text-align: left;
            padding: 10px 14px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #6b7280;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.04em;
        }

        .compliance-table td {
            padding: 10px 14px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #111827;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6;
        }

        .status-pass {
            color: #059669;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .standards-section {
            background: #ecfdf5;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 24px 0;
        }

        .standards-title {
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #065f46;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.04em;
        }

        .standards-list {
            padding-left: 20px;
        }

        .standards-list li {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #065f46;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }

        .validity-box {
            background: #eff6ff;
            border: 1px solid #bfdbfe;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 16px 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .validity-box .label {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #3b82f6;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.04em;
        }

        .validity-box .value {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #1e40af;
        }

        .signature-section {
            margin-top: 40px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-end;
        }

        .seal-block {
            width: 35%;
        }

        .seal-box {
            border: 1px solid #d1d5db;
            border-radius: 8px;
            height: 72px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #9ca3af;
            margin-top: 8px;
        }

        .sig-block {
            width: 40%;
        }

        .sig-label {
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #6b7280;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.04em;
        }

        .sig-line {
            border-top: 1px solid #d1d5db;
            padding-top: 6px;
        }

        .sig-name {
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #111827;
        }

        .sig-role {
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #6b7280;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 48px;
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 24px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            color: #9ca3af;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="letterhead">
        <div class="company-name">{{companyName}}</div>
        <div class="company-detail">{{{companyAddress}}}{{#if companyPhone}} | {{companyPhone}}{{/if}}{{#if
            companyEmail}} | {{companyEmail}}{{/if}}</div>
    </div>

    <div class="doc-title-wrap">
        <div class="doc-title">COMPLIANCE</div>
        <div class="doc-subtitle">Certificate of Compliance</div>
        <div class="compliant-badge">✓ Certified Compliant</div>
    </div>

    <div class="cert-meta">
        <div class="cert-meta-item">
            <div class="label">Certificate No.</div>
            <div class="value">{{#if certificateNumber}}{{certificateNumber}}{{else}}CC-2024-001{{/if}}</div>
        </div>
        <div class="cert-meta-item">
            <div class="label">Issue Date</div>
            <div class="value">{{issueDate}}</div>
        </div>
        <div class="cert-meta-item">
            <div class="label">Valid Until</div>
            <div class="value">{{expiryDate}}</div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="entity-card">
        <div class="entity-label">Certified Entity</div>
        <div class="entity-name">{{#if certifiedEntity}}{{certifiedEntity}}{{else}}{{companyName}}{{/if}}</div>
        <div class="entity-detail">{{{companyAddress}}}{{#if registrationNumber}}<br><strong>Registration No:</strong>
            {{registrationNumber}}{{/if}}{{#if gstNumber}}<br><strong>GST:</strong> {{gstNumber}}{{/if}}</div>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <p>This is to certify that the above-named entity has been found to be in compliance with the applicable
            regulations, standards, and requirements as specified below. This certification is issued following a
            thorough review and assessment conducted by the authorized compliance officer.</p>

        <div class="standards-section">
            <div class="standards-title">Applicable Standards & Regulations</div>
            <ul class="standards-list">
                <li>{{{complianceStandard}}}</li>
                {{#if additionalStandards}}<li>{{{additionalStandards}}}</li>{{/if}}
            </ul>
        </div>

        <p><strong>Scope of Compliance:</strong> {{{complianceScope}}}</p>

        <p>The assessment confirmed that appropriate policies, procedures, and controls are in place and are operating
            effectively to ensure compliance with the above-stated standards and regulations.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="validity-box">
        <div class="label">Certificate Validity Period</div>
        <div class="value">{{issueDate}} — {{expiryDate}}</div>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <p>This certificate is issued based on the information and evidence available at the time of assessment. Any
            material changes to operations, processes, or organizational structure may necessitate re-evaluation. The
            certified entity is responsible for maintaining compliance throughout the validity period.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="signature-section">
        <div class="seal-block">
            <div style="font-size: 11px; color: #6b7280; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.04em;">Company
                Seal</div>
            <div class="seal-box">OFFICIAL SEAL</div>
        </div>
        <div class="sig-block">
            <div class="sig-label">Compliance Officer</div>
            <div class="sig-line">
                <div class="sig-name">{{#if complianceOfficer}}{{complianceOfficer}}{{else}}Compliance Officer{{/if}}
                </div>
                <div class="sig-role">{{#if officerDesignation}}{{officerDesignation}}{{else}}Chief Compliance
                    Officer{{/if}}<br>{{companyName}}</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>This certificate is system-generated. Verify authenticity at {{#if
            companyEmail}}{{companyEmail}}{{else}}compliance@company.com{{/if}}</p>
        <p>{{companyName}} — Compliance Division</p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>